<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="4ab2e3bb-3519-484f-b1ca-99fafa6f591b" >

    <p>Internal Audit Services at Ryerson University recognizes the importance of a collaborative and constructive working relationship throughout the audit process. Our objective is to have your continued involvement at every stage so you understand what Internal Audit Services is doing and why, while trying to minimize disruption of your daily activities.</p> 
<h2>Stages of an audit</h2> 
<p>A typical audit is comprised of the following stages:</p>
    





</div>
